                    {
                      "type": "Label",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "fontSize": 26,
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontColor": "#0B1220",
                      "text": "section_contract_heading"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "Label",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "topMargin": 12,
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontColor": "#475467",
                      "text": "section_contract_body"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "CodeBlock",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "topMargin": 16,
                      "code": "// docs/screens/json/counter.spec.json\n{\n  \"metadata\": { \"name\": \"Counter\", \"platforms\": [\"web\"] },\n  \"stateManagement\": {\n    \"uiVariables\": [{ \"name\": \"count\", \"type\": \"Int\", \"initial\": \"0\" }],\n    \"eventHandlers\": [{ \"name\": \"onIncrement\" }]\n  }\n}",
                      "language": "json",
                      "filename": "counter.spec.json",
                      "showLineNumbers": true,
                      "copyable": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "Label",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "topMargin": 16,
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontColor": "#475467",
                      "text": "section_contract_body_2"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "View",
                  "orientation": "vertical",
                  "id": "section_drift_gate",
                  "width": "matchParent",
                  "height": "wrapContent",
                  "paddings": [
                    24,
                    32,
                    24,
                    32
                  ],
                  "background": "#FFFFFF",
                  "child": [
                    {
                      "type": "Label",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "fontSize": 26,
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontColor": "#0B1220",
                      "text": "section_drift_heading"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "Label",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "topMargin": 12,
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontColor": "#475467",
                      "text": "section_drift_body"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "CodeBlock",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "topMargin": 16,
                      "code": "$ jui verify --fail-on-diff\n\n# Screen        | Expected | Actual | Match | Missing | Extra | TypeMM | %\n# ─────────────┼──────────┼────────┼───────┼─────────┼───────┼────────┼────\n# Counter       | 12       | 12     | ✓     | 0       | 0     | 0      | 100%\n# Home          | 47       | 47     | ✓     | 0       | 0     | 0      | 100%\n#\n# Total: match=2, missing=0, extra=0, type_mismatch=0\n# ✓ No drift detected. Exit 0.",
                      "language": "bash",
                      "filename": "CI log",
                      "showLineNumbers": false,
                      "copyable": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "View",
                  "orientation": "vertical",
                  "id": "section_agent",
                  "width": "matchParent",
                  "height": "wrapContent",
                  "paddings": [
                    24,
                    32,
                    24,
                    32
                  ],
                  "background": "#F9FAFB",
                  "child": [
                    {
                      "type": "Label",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "fontSize": 26,
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontColor": "#0B1220",
                      "text": "section_agent_heading"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "Label",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "topMargin": 12,
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontColor": "#475467",
                      "text": "section_agent_body"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "CodeBlock",
                      "width": "matchParent",
                      "height": "wrapContent",
                      "topMargin": 16,
                      "code": "You: implement the submit action on the login screen\n\nAgent:\n  1. mcp.read_spec('login')                  → gets uiVariables, handlers, transitions\n  2. mcp.read_layout('login')                → confirms Button with onClick=\"@{onSubmit}\"\n  3. mcp.lookup_attribute('onClick', 'Button') → confirms handler signature: () -> Void\n  4. edit src/viewmodels/LoginViewModel.ts   → implement onSubmit()\n  5. mcp.jui_build()                         → zero warnings\n  6. mcp.jui_verify()                        → no drift\n\nNo file reading, no guessing attribute names, no surprises.",
                      "language": "text",
                      "filename": "agent trace (condensed)",
                      "showLineNumbers": false,
                      "copyable": false
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "View",
                  "orientation": "vertical",
                  "id": "section_tradeoff",
                  "width": "matchParent",
                  "height": "wrapContent",
